     By creating our marketplace, Kintessia, we were able to launch a
     completely disruptive business in the group, in just a few short
     months. Thanks to the training provided before the launch our
     account managers could take charge of the Wizaplace back office
     quickly. The follow-up and support we receive allow functionalities
     and our user experience to be developed.

   Marie d'Avezac

   Marketplace manager, Kintessia

     We were looking for a partner whose business model would enable us
     to invest at a lower cost, while at the same time being able to
     support us in the scalability of our platform. Wizaplace convinced
     us not only thanks to its economic model and its seriousness during
     the project comprehension stage for adapting the commercial offer,
     but also due to its teams’ credibility and its board composed of
     well known figures from the profession.

   Faustin Falcon

   President, pecheur.com

     Energy Bay has grown from an idea to a first version accessible to
     our users in just a few months, not only thanks to the Wizaplace
     Back-Office, which has allowed us to reduce our time-to-market, but
     also to Front-end development, integrated by Altran. all supported
     by a scalablity agility framework. The first operational and manager
     feedback is positive!

